Package: clusterpathRcpp
Type: Package
Title: Fast agglomerative convex clustering, original Rcpp implementation
Version: 1.1
Author: Toby Dylan Hocking
Maintainer: Toby Dylan Hocking <toby@sg.cs.titech.ac.jp>
Description: Implements the clusterpath, a clustering method in which all
 the clusters are solutions to a convex optimization problem with fusion
 penalties. This package uses the original Rcpp bindings
 to wrap the C++ implementation.
License: GPL-3
Depends: R (>= 2.11.0), Rcpp (>= 0.9.9), lattice, ggplot2, plyr, reshape2, 
	 latticeExtra, Matrix, grid
Suggests: rgl, directlabels, mclust, multicore
LinkingTo: Rcpp

